---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import scottPhoto from '../assets/scott-photo-2.jpg';
---

<Layout title="About Scott Armbruster | AI Implementation Specialist" description="Learn about Scott Armbruster's background in AI implementation, enterprise consulting, and education.">
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="pt-32 pb-20 px-6">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <div>
          <p class="text-blue-400 text-sm font-semibold tracking-wide uppercase mb-6">
            About Me
          </p>

          <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold mb-6 leading-tight">
            Hi, I'm{' '}
            <span class="text-white">
              Scott Armbruster
            </span>
          </h1>

          <p class="text-xl text-slate-300 mb-6">
            I've spent 23+ years in technology and 10+ years consulting Fortune 500 companies.
            Now I help professionals build AI-powered income streams and organizations deploy
            AI systems that deliver real results.
          </p>

          <p class="text-lg text-slate-400 mb-8">
            My mission is simple: bridge the gap between learning and doing. Too many people
            get stuck consuming content about AI without ever implementing anything. I'm here
            to change that.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="flex justify-center">
          <div class="bg-slate-900 rounded-2xl p-8">
            <Image
              src={scottPhoto}
              alt="Scott Armbruster"
              width={256}
              height={256}
              class="w-64 h-64 mx-auto rounded-full object-cover object-top"
              format="webp"
              quality={80}
            />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Background Section -->
  <section class="py-20 px-6 border-t border-slate-800/60">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-12 text-center">My Journey</h2>

      <div class="space-y-12">
        <div class="flex gap-6">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-blue-600/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 20l4-16m4 4l4 4-4 4M6 16l-4-4 4-4"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">23+ Years in Technology</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-400">
              Started building software systems before most people knew what the internet was.
              Watched technologies come and go, learned what matters and what's just hype.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex gap-6">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-blue-600/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 21V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v16m14 0h2m-2 0h-5m-9 0H3m2 0h5M9 7h1m-1 4h1m4-4h1m-1 4h1m-5 10v-5a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v5m-4 0h4"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">10+ Years Consulting Fortune 500</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-400">
              Helped enterprise organizations implement technology solutions that actually work
              in the real world. Learned what separates successful implementations from failures.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex gap-6">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-blue-600/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.988-2.386l-.548-.547z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">AI Implementation Focus</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-400">
              When AI emerged as the next major technology shift, I dove deep. Not just learning
              the tools, but figuring out how to actually implement them for real business results.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Values Section -->
  <section class="py-20 px-6">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-12 text-center">What I Believe</h2>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-slate-900 border border-slate-800 rounded-xl p-8">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4 text-blue-400">Implementation Over Theory</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-400">
            Knowledge without action is just entertainment. Everything I teach is designed
            to get you implementing, not just learning.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-slate-900 border border-slate-800 rounded-xl p-8">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4 text-blue-400">Results Over Hype</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-400">
            I'm not interested in what's trendy. I focus on what works, what delivers
            measurable results, and what creates real value.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-slate-900 border border-slate-800 rounded-xl p-8">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4 text-blue-400">Accessibility Over Gatekeeping</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-400">
            AI shouldn't be reserved for tech elites. I believe anyone with the drive
            to learn can master these tools and build something meaningful.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="py-20 px-6 border-t border-slate-800/60">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6">Let's Work Together</h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-slate-300 mb-8">
        Whether you're looking to build AI skills or implement AI systems for your
        organization, I'm here to help.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <a
          href="/services"
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 px-8 py-4 rounded-lg text-lg font-semibold transition"
        >
          Explore Services
        </a>
        <a
          href="/contact"
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 bg-slate-800 hover:bg-slate-700 px-8 py-4 rounded-lg text-lg font-semibold transition"
        >
          Get in Touch
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
